text: Mojca Mavrič (born 8 October 1980) is a Slovenian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Slovenia Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
